Document: FBXState
Path: godot/classes/class_fbxstate.rst
Summary: Configures use of geometry helper nodes during FBX import to preserve original 3D model transformations

Property: allow_geometry_helper_nodes (bool) = false
Method: set_allow_geometry_helper_nodes(value: bool)
Method: get_allow_geometry_helper_nodes() → bool
Description: If true, the import process uses auxiliary geometry helper nodes to preserve pivots and transformations of the original 3D model during import. These nodes help maintain the spatial relationships and orientation of model components as they were in the source file.